---
---
<section id="about" class="py-24 md:py-32 px-6 bg-gray-50 dark:bg-neutral-900/50">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
        
        <!-- Top Section: Bio & Photo -->
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-12 lg:gap-16 items-center mb-20">
            <!-- Left Side: Bio (lg:col-span-8) -->
            <div class="lg:col-span-8">
                <p class="text-sm text-neutral-500 dark:text-neutral-400 mb-3 tracking-wide uppercase font-semibold">About Me</p>
                <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-neutral-900 dark:text-white mb-6 tracking-tight leading-tight">
                    Passionate about crafting digital excellence
                </h2>
                <div class="space-y-6 text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400 leading-relaxed text-base md:text-lg">
                    <p>
                        With over 8 years of experience in web engineering, I specialize in building digital products that blend high-performance backend systems with intuitive, user-centric interfaces.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        My focus is on pragmatic execution—transforming ideas into functional, client-ready applications without getting bogged down in over-engineering. I strive to build systems that solve real business problems immediately.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        Beyond writing code, I am deeply involved in developer communities, actively exploring emerging technologies and adapting to new development frameworks to stay at the cutting edge.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Right Side: Greyscale Profile Photo (lg:col-span-4) -->
            <div class="lg:col-span-4 flex justify-center lg:justify-end">
                <div class="relative rounded-3xl overflow-hidden aspect-square w-full max-w-[280px] border-4 border-white dark:border-neutral-800 shadow-2xl group">
                    <img 
                        src="/assets/images/photo.jpeg" 
                        alt="Muhammad Dawil Akmami" 
                        class="w-full h-full object-cover grayscale hover:grayscale-0 transition-all duration-700 ease-out scale-102 group-hover:scale-105" 
                    />
                    <!-- Overlay shadow/glow -->
                    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-neutral-950/10 dark:bg-neutral-950/20 pointer-events-none group-hover:opacity-0 transition-opacity duration-500"></div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Bottom Section: Core Pillars & Philosophy Cards (3 Column Grid) -->
        <div>
            <p class="text-sm text-neutral-500 dark:text-neutral-400 mb-3 tracking-wide uppercase font-semibold text-center lg:text-left">Core Values</p>
            <h3 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-neutral-900 dark:text-white mb-10 text-center lg:text-left">
                My Product &amp; Engineering Philosophy
            </h3>

            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
                <!-- Pillar 1: Fast Delivery & Agility (Replaced Clean Code) -->
                <div class="p-6 md:p-8 rounded-3xl bg-white dark:bg-neutral-900/40 border border-neutral-100 dark:border-neutral-800/80 shadow-xs hover:border-neutral-300 dark:hover:border-neutral-700 hover:shadow-md transition-all duration-300 flex flex-col gap-6">
                    <div class="p-3 rounded-2xl bg-neutral-100 dark:bg-neutral-800 text-neutral-900 dark:text-white shrink-0 self-start">
                        <svg
                            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                            width="24"
                            height="24"
                            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                            fill="none"
                            stroke="currentColor"
                            stroke-width="2"
                            stroke-linecap="round"
                            stroke-linejoin="round"
                            class="lucide lucide-rocket-icon lucide-rocket size-5">
                            <path d="M12 15v5s3.03-.55 4-2c1.08-1.62 0-5 0-5"></path>
                            <path d="M4.5 16.5c-1.5 1.26-2 5-2 5s3.74-.5 5-2c.71-.84.7-2.13-.09-2.91a2.18 2.18 0 0 0-2.91-.09"></path>
                            <path d="M9 12a22 22 0 0 1 2-3.95A12.88 12.88 0 0 1 22 2c0 2.72-.78 7.5-6 11a22.4 22.4 0 0 1-4 2z"></path>
                            <path d="M9 12H4s.55-3.03 2-4c1.62-1.08 5 .05 5 .05"></path>
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <h4 class="text-lg font-bold text-neutral-900 dark:text-white">Fast Delivery &amp; Agility</h4>
                        <p class="text-sm text-neutral-500 dark:text-neutral-400 mt-2 leading-relaxed">
                            Focusing on pragmatism and speed-to-market. I turn concepts into functional, working MVPs rapidly, prioritizing product iteration and swift launch cycles.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Pillar 2: User-Centric UI/UX -->
                <div class="p-6 md:p-8 rounded-3xl bg-white dark:bg-neutral-900/40 border border-neutral-100 dark:border-neutral-800/80 shadow-xs hover:border-neutral-300 dark:hover:border-neutral-700 hover:shadow-md transition-all duration-300 flex flex-col gap-6">
                    <div class="p-3 rounded-2xl bg-neutral-100 dark:bg-neutral-800 text-neutral-900 dark:text-white shrink-0 self-start">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-layout w-5 h-5">
                            <rect width="18" height="18" x="3" y="3" rx="2"></rect>
                            <path d="M3 9h18"></path>
                            <path d="M9 21V9"></path>
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <h4 class="text-lg font-bold text-neutral-900 dark:text-white">User-Centric UI/UX</h4>
                        <p class="text-sm text-neutral-500 dark:text-neutral-400 mt-2 leading-relaxed">
                            Bridging the gap between design and engineering. I build clean, highly responsive, and accessible interfaces that align perfectly with user behavior and business needs.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Pillar 3: Performance & Optimization -->
                <div class="p-6 md:p-8 rounded-3xl bg-white dark:bg-neutral-900/40 border border-neutral-100 dark:border-neutral-800/80 shadow-xs hover:border-neutral-300 dark:hover:border-neutral-700 hover:shadow-md transition-all duration-300 flex flex-col gap-6">
                    <div class="p-3 rounded-2xl bg-neutral-100 dark:bg-neutral-800 text-neutral-900 dark:text-white shrink-0 self-start">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-zap w-5 h-5">
                            <path d="M4 14a1 1 0 0 1-.78-1.63l9.9-10.2a.5.5 0 0 1 .86.46L12.14 9.5a.5.5 0 0 0 .34.62l6.74 1.38a1 1 0 0 1 .78 1.63l-9.9 10.2a.5.5 0 0 1-.86-.46l1.86-6.88a.5.5 0 0 0-.34-.62Z"></path>
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <h4 class="text-lg font-bold text-neutral-900 dark:text-white">Performance &amp; Speed</h4>
                        <p class="text-sm text-neutral-500 dark:text-neutral-400 mt-2 leading-relaxed">
                            Ensuring that speed is never compromised. I build lightweight, optimized applications with clean Core Web Vitals to deliver optimal user experiences on any device.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

    </div>
</section>
